æFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."‡
›IN LOVING MEMORY OF PETER WADE
CHAIRMAN OF THE ASSOCIATION OF ISLAND COMMUNITIES
AND LATER HEAD OF PUBLIC AFFAIRS FOR CANARY WHARF GROUP.
HE WORKED ON THE DOCKSIDE HERE LONG BEFORE THIS DEVELOPMENT WAS PLANNED.
WITH GRATITUDE FROM HIS FAMILY AND COLLEAGUES KNOWING THAT HIS SERVICE TO LOCAL PEOPLE
AND TO CANARY WHARF WILL ALWAYS BE REMEMBERED."„
